Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Sampaloc Elementary School in the Municipality of Sampaloc, Province of Quezon, to Medardo L. Tumagay Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 865
An Act Changing the Name of the Sampaloc Elementary School in the Municipality of Sampaloc, Province of Quezon, to Medardo L. Tumagay Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Sampaloc Elementary School located in the Municipality of Sampaloc, Province of Quezon, is hereby changed to Medardo L. Tumagay Elementary School.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.1Ã¢wphi1
Approved: April 27, 1984
